Title: Iron Fortress Mk II
Description:
A fortress with a lot of mark II armored bots, a spidertrons 5000, flameraptors and other enemies.
Most of the enemies are separated by walls, which makes the level pretty easy.

Features:
1. Main area
2. Side yards
2. Roof
3. Bottom area

Difficulties:
1 silver, 1 gold, 1 diamond, 1 titanium, 1 uranium.

Have fun!
